title: Hand-holding Instagram travellers go on honeymoon
text:
Hand-holding Instagram travellers go on honeymoon Last updated 11:44, July 22 2015 Instagram/muradosmann 
Russian photographer Murad Osmann and his wife television journalist Nataly Zakxarova honeymoon in the Maldives 
The famous #followmeto hand-holding couple who travel the world together have gone on their honeymoon, continuing to post gorgeous travel instagrams along the way. 
Russian photographer Murad Osmann has created a career and won millions of fans by of posting stunning globe-trotting pictures while being led around the world by his wife, television journalist Nataly Zakxarova. 
Their wedding photos were enough to make anyone want to pack their bags, and now they've updated Instragram with breathtaking photos from their honeymoon. From the sunny beaches of the Maldives to the bright lights of Vegas, the duo certainly know how to inspire wanderlust in the rest of us.
